WEBVTT

00:01.540 --> 00:03.280
Previously on Damages...

00:03.290 --> 00:04.520
Did you get any word from patty?

00:04.530 --> 00:06.130
I've told her that she's
got to come back here.

00:06.140 --> 00:07.689
She doesn't want to come back.

00:07.700 --> 00:11.530
You think patty tried to
kill you to protect herself?

00:11.540 --> 00:14.340
I am trying to settle this case.

00:14.350 --> 00:15.230
Try harder.

00:15.240 --> 00:16.860
She's divorcing me.

00:16.870 --> 00:18.660
Maybe I'll tell him about
you and gregory malina.

00:18.670 --> 00:21.040
Give me five minutes,ray.

00:21.050 --> 00:24.300
I think george moore engineered
this whole hit- and-run.

00:24.310 --> 00:26.810
I think he leaked arlington
to get you to settle.

00:26.820 --> 00:29.660
George moore made a big show
of going after frobisher.

00:29.670 --> 00:31.100
But you didn't believe he was?

00:31.110 --> 00:33.110
I could get killed for what I told you.

00:33.120 --> 00:36.290
If there's a connection between you
and arthur frobisher,we will find it.

00:36.300 --> 00:37.350
I spoke with george moore.

00:37.360 --> 00:39.980
How could you be so stupid?

00:39.990 --> 00:42.450
Don't bother coming back.

00:43.740 --> 00:46.070
Thanks for the advice...

00:46.080 --> 00:48.540
but I guess I won't be
needing this anymore.

00:48.550 --> 00:50.250
What happened?

00:50.260 --> 00:52.820
I told her I was sick of her bullshit.

00:52.830 --> 00:54.050
You what?

00:54.060 --> 00:56.910
Ellen,you're a first-year associate.

00:56.920 --> 01:00.330
When patty was my age,do you think she
would have tolerated a boss like her?

01:00.340 --> 01:01.460
No.

01:01.470 --> 01:03.630
Then why should I?

01:03.640 --> 01:05.810
Was this about the case?

01:05.820 --> 01:07.090
Sort of.

01:07.100 --> 01:09.540
I uncovered some evidence on my own...

01:09.550 --> 01:12.740
But patty was more interested in
putting me in my place than what I found.

01:12.750 --> 01:14.300
I see,mm-hmm.

01:14.310 --> 01:17.140
She says it's all about
the case,but it's not.

01:17.150 --> 01:19.000
It's about her and her mind games.

01:19.010 --> 01:20.130
Yes.

01:20.140 --> 01:23.320
I want the clients to
win their case,but...

01:23.330 --> 01:25.260
I'm not going to be
patty's punching bag.

01:25.270 --> 01:27.780
Oh,you'll bounce back.

01:27.790 --> 01:30.550
Which is why I'm here,mr.Nye.

01:31.160 --> 01:33.360
I need a job.

01:34.090 --> 01:37.120
The law will always be here,ellen.

01:37.130 --> 01:40.230
But,um,your wedding
is coming up,isn't it?

01:40.240 --> 01:41.690
Yes.

01:41.700 --> 01:45.120
You know,I made similar
mistakes early in my career.

01:45.130 --> 01:47.600
Never took a honeymoon.

01:47.610 --> 01:51.340
Don't let your life pass you by.

