03:41.660 --> 03:44.030
Babe,this is a nightmare.

03:44.040 --> 03:45.380
What is?

03:45.390 --> 03:46.670
The seating arrangement.

03:46.680 --> 03:50.770
It's more complicated than the bar exam.

03:50.780 --> 03:54.680
Can I sit your cousin
jake next to heather?

03:54.690 --> 03:56.980
Why are you always trying
to pimp heather out,huh?

03:56.990 --> 03:58.940
I just thought,you know,they both...

03:58.950 --> 04:00.030
they both love hiking...

04:00.040 --> 04:02.520
and narcotics.

04:02.740 --> 04:04.240
they have lots to talk about.

04:04.250 --> 04:06.420
How'd it go with nye?

04:06.430 --> 04:08.500
He wouldn't give me a job.

04:08.510 --> 04:10.670
He told me to take a vacation.

04:11.000 --> 04:13.770
I love this man.

04:14.990 --> 04:17.829
All right,I will see you later.

04:17.839 --> 04:19.480
- Okay?
- Okay.

04:23.620 --> 04:24.990
Hello,david.

04:25.000 --> 04:26.960
Patty.

04:28.910 --> 04:31.190
May I come in?

04:41.160 --> 04:43.810
Do you want to call me later?

04:43.820 --> 04:46.550
Yeah. I will.

04:54.730 --> 04:57.390
I was wondering when you would show up.

05:01.750 --> 05:03.800
You impressed me with this.

05:03.810 --> 05:05.720
I wasn't trying to.

05:06.160 --> 05:09.230
Just take the information and use it.

05:11.310 --> 05:15.430
It's all very intriguing,but
how does it help our case?

05:15.440 --> 05:20.050
George moore was heading up the sec
investigation into frobisher's company,

05:20.060 --> 05:22.500
but according to a
former sec investigator...

05:22.510 --> 05:23.700
Laura watkins.

05:23.710 --> 05:24.720
I met with her.

05:24.730 --> 05:28.270
She believed that moore was making a big
show of wanting to take down frobisher,

05:28.280 --> 05:31.880
but behind the scenes he was
torpedoing the investigation.

05:31.890 --> 05:33.850
And all the
rest of this--

05:33.860 --> 05:37.380
the hotel records,the rental
car receipts,a flight manifest...

05:37.390 --> 05:40.890
All show that george moore
was in jacksonville,florida

05:40.900 --> 05:43.530
the weekend before
frobisher sold his stock.

05:43.540 --> 05:47.910
Moore drove down to palm
beach to tip off frobisher.

05:49.730 --> 05:51.970
It's a nice theory.

05:53.020 --> 05:54.270
No proof.

05:54.280 --> 05:56.000
Use it anyway.

05:56.010 --> 05:57.630
Put pressure on moore.

05:57.640 --> 05:59.130
To do what?

05:59.140 --> 06:01.330
Get frobisher to settle.

06:01.340 --> 06:04.190
I could never understand
why moore leaked arlington,

06:04.200 --> 06:06.840
but now it makes perfect sense.

06:06.850 --> 06:09.900
He must be afraid of what
would come out in a trial.

06:09.910 --> 06:14.450
Moore wants the whole case to go away,and
if he knows that you're closing in on him...

06:14.460 --> 06:18.320
He'll give us more dirt we
can use against frobisher.

06:20.190 --> 06:22.450
So...

06:23.070 --> 06:25.590
we need to go back to moore.

06:27.180 --> 06:29.330
I think so.

06:29.340 --> 06:33.730
And you're the only lawyer
in my firm he'll talk to.

06:42.060 --> 06:44.630
It's a nice apartment.

06:45.640 --> 06:48.040
Isn't it?

06:54.660 --> 06:56.530
Go back to moore.

07:02.360 --> 07:04.670
And...

07:04.680 --> 07:09.370
of course you can have your job back.

07:10.320 --> 07:12.770
I don't want it.

07:14.450 --> 07:17.170
But I'll talk to moore.

07:17.550 --> 07:20.330
I want you to win this case.

07:23.980 --> 07:27.090
Our court date--
six weeks,folks.

07:27.100 --> 07:31.100
Tom's running point,so if he
needs you to do something,do it.

07:31.110 --> 07:32.670
Exhibits,witness prep.

07:32.680 --> 07:34.570
It is deadline time.

07:34.580 --> 07:37.700
Felicia,do you have the expert list?

07:37.710 --> 07:39.630
You'll get it tomorrow.

07:40.320 --> 07:41.680
That's it.

07:41.690 --> 07:44.100
Make your mothers proud.

07:45.750 --> 07:47.680
- Where was ellen this morning?
- I don't know.

07:47.690 --> 07:48.650
Maybe she wasn't feeling well.

07:48.660 --> 07:51.080
Tom,half the office saw
her storm out the other day.

07:51.090 --> 07:51.970
Did patty fire her?

07:51.980 --> 07:54.500
Just focus on the case.

07:54.510 --> 07:55.600
Everyone's talking about it.

07:55.610 --> 07:56.870
- What are we supposed to tell them?
- Whatever you want.

07:56.880 --> 07:58.260
Tell them ellen's dead.

07:58.270 --> 08:00.960
Just get me the goddamn expert list.

08:04.060 --> 08:05.640
I hope she was fired.

08:05.650 --> 08:07.190
I never liked her.

08:09.200 --> 08:10.820
Ray?

08:10.830 --> 08:11.970
Hey.

08:11.980 --> 08:13.940
What are you doing here?

08:13.950 --> 08:16.680
I thought you could use some lunch.

08:18.020 --> 08:19.520
what do we got here?

08:19.530 --> 08:23.590
A nice filet,some asparagus,and
some blackberry cobbler.

08:23.600 --> 08:25.930
sweetie,this is stupendous.

08:25.940 --> 08:27.430
I finished my meetings this morning,

08:27.440 --> 08:30.480
and i just realized
how much I missed you.

08:30.490 --> 08:33.630
I know,I know,I'm sorry.

08:33.640 --> 08:36.240
This case has just taken over my life.

08:36.250 --> 08:39.980
They all do,ray,but this one...

08:40.789 --> 08:43.179
this one's different.

08:43.669 --> 08:46.250
I worry about you.

08:46.760 --> 08:49.280
You're so quiet these days.

08:49.290 --> 08:50.460
what?

08:50.470 --> 08:52.660
You never accused me of that before.

08:52.670 --> 08:54.700
Well,it's true.

08:54.930 --> 08:59.050
Soon as the case is over,I'll be
a regular ol' chatterbox again.

08:59.060 --> 09:00.710
Well,that'll be nice.

09:00.720 --> 09:04.730
We'll take a few days,go
see your sister in tacoma.

09:04.740 --> 09:06.380
I'll believe that when I see it.

09:06.390 --> 09:08.040
I promise.

09:08.050 --> 09:10.490
Sit,sit,eat.

09:12.420 --> 09:14.920
Oh,that smells good.

09:16.830 --> 09:19.060
********

09:21.600 --> 09:23.320
MAY 2002

09:23.650 --> 09:25.110
More wine?

09:26.630 --> 09:28.220
Why not?

09:29.390 --> 09:32.160
We're going to be closing soon,so...

09:34.480 --> 09:36.780
Looks like I'm your last customer.

09:36.790 --> 09:40.450
I suppose I just lost track of the time.

09:40.460 --> 09:42.890
You're always coming in here
with work. What do you do?

09:42.900 --> 09:44.780
I'm an attorney.

09:46.520 --> 09:48.920
You know,I don't believe
I've ever caught your name.

09:48.930 --> 09:49.850
Greg.

09:49.860 --> 09:51.290
Ray.

09:56.070 --> 09:57.770
A blackout?

09:58.150 --> 10:00.680
You were probably still in kindergarten.

10:00.690 --> 10:05.810
This was 1977,the very
first week I arrived.

10:06.380 --> 10:09.580
An auspicious debut. Shit.

10:10.250 --> 10:11.660
Guess when I got here.

10:11.670 --> 10:12.840
When?

10:12.850 --> 10:15.120
Last september.

10:15.130 --> 10:16.970
You don't say. Yeah.

10:16.980 --> 10:18.420
Before or after?

10:18.430 --> 10:20.230
Just before.

10:20.240 --> 10:23.450
It almost made my change my
mind,but then I thought...

10:23.480 --> 10:25.700
if I leave now...

10:25.710 --> 10:28.220
They win. Right.

10:29.440 --> 10:31.080
I probably should have left,though.

10:31.090 --> 10:32.160
Why's that?

10:32.170 --> 10:33.690
I don't know,I...

10:34.140 --> 10:35.770
I just can'T...

10:35.780 --> 10:37.930
get going,you know?

10:37.940 --> 10:42.460
I live in a shithole,and i
barely make enough to pay my rent.

10:43.790 --> 10:46.870
Why did you decide to move
here in the first place?

10:47.360 --> 10:49.710
I'll try anything once,I guess.

10:52.240 --> 10:54.000
Oh,I'm sorry.

10:58.590 --> 11:00.050
That's my wife.

11:00.060 --> 11:01.610
You're married?

11:01.620 --> 11:03.380
Never seen her; you never bring her in.

11:03.390 --> 11:08.380
Oh,I come in here to work,clear my head.

11:09.020 --> 11:11.910
You like being an attorney?

11:11.920 --> 11:16.720
I like the relationship
between attorney and client.

11:17.950 --> 11:22.860
There's an intimacy there,a trust.

11:23.290 --> 11:28.010
Someone puts himself in your hands.

11:29.050 --> 11:31.060
And you like that.

11:31.280 --> 11:33.050
I do.

11:51.810 --> 11:53.390
What the hell are you doing here?

11:53.400 --> 11:55.850
Oh,uh,a couple downstairs
said the ceiling was dripping.

11:55.860 --> 11:57.820
Just,um...

11:57.830 --> 11:59.720
checking for a leak.

12:06.010 --> 12:07.770
And the lamp?

12:08.190 --> 12:10.360
Noticed a bulb was out.

12:11.900 --> 12:14.310
Does ellen know that you're here?

12:14.320 --> 12:15.760
No.

12:16.490 --> 12:19.890
Patty hewes told me to
extra special care of you.

12:19.900 --> 12:23.760
Next time,you call me.

12:30.860 --> 12:33.340
Don't ever do this again.

12:38.060 --> 12:39.430
6 DAYS LATER

12:39.440 --> 12:43.360
You have 57 new messages.

12:43.370 --> 12:45.470
Patty,it's tom.

12:46.390 --> 12:47.800
it's tom.

12:48.910 --> 12:51.800
I'm in rome now.I'm worried about you...

12:52.560 --> 12:54.440
it's tom...

12:55.380 --> 12:57.840
Yeah,mom,I'm up at
henry'S.Everything's fine...

12:58.850 --> 13:00.170
I don't know how to tell you this.

13:00.180 --> 13:02.540
I just got a call from hollis nye.

13:02.550 --> 13:05.030
Somehow,ellen's in jail.

13:10.540 --> 13:11.670
I don't know how to tell you this.

13:11.680 --> 13:14.150
I just got a call from hollis nye.

13:14.160 --> 13:16.390
Somehow,ellen's in jail.

13:16.400 --> 13:19.120
She was arrested for killing david.

14:04.000 --> 14:06.000
How was sawgrass?

14:06.520 --> 14:07.760
I'm sorry?

14:07.770 --> 14:10.910
Did you hit the green on
17 or end up in the drink?

14:10.920 --> 14:12.970
Depends on when you're talking about.

14:12.980 --> 14:15.190
June,2002.

14:15.200 --> 14:18.990
You were in jacksonville,florida the
weekend before frobisher dumped his stock.

14:19.000 --> 14:20.670
Ah,yes.

14:20.680 --> 14:22.970
I hit the green.

14:22.980 --> 14:24.980
I'm sure you did.

14:24.990 --> 14:27.910
Then you drove four hours to palm
beach and tipped off frobisher that

14:27.920 --> 14:32.910
the sec was about to release a
report damning his company's finances.

14:32.920 --> 14:34.800
Frobisher give you a nice kickback?

14:34.810 --> 14:37.880
I was trying to prosecute
arthur frobisher.

14:37.890 --> 14:40.840
Not according to laura watkins.

14:42.070 --> 14:43.050
Look,I don't know what you think...

14:43.060 --> 14:44.870
I think you want this case to be over,

14:44.880 --> 14:47.180
and i think that we can help each other.

14:47.190 --> 14:49.170
Give us something on frobisher.

14:49.180 --> 14:51.040
And if I don't?

14:51.050 --> 14:54.600
Then patty hewes
starts looking into you.

14:54.610 --> 14:57.990
Your finances,your
investments,your bank accounts--

14:58.000 --> 15:00.910
anything you have hidden,she'll find it.

15:00.920 --> 15:03.590
I told you,I can't give you frobisher.

15:03.600 --> 15:05.010
But I can give you somebody.

15:05.020 --> 15:06.830
Who?

15:06.840 --> 15:09.690
Same time,tomorrow night,meet me here.

15:09.700 --> 15:12.180
I'll bring you a present.

15:56.870 --> 15:58.530
Jesus...

16:00.610 --> 16:02.270
you scared me.

16:03.500 --> 16:06.670
You're so cute when you
think you're alone. Yeah?

16:07.370 --> 16:09.790
Ugh,I'm living life in reverse.

16:09.800 --> 16:12.390
First breakfast then bed.

16:15.270 --> 16:16.620
What's that?

16:16.630 --> 16:19.330
It's our first wedding gift.

16:19.340 --> 16:23.030
Don't get too excited,though. It's
from aunt marge and uncle fran.

16:25.670 --> 16:28.150
A garden gnome?

16:28.850 --> 16:30.990
We live in an apartment.

16:31.000 --> 16:34.650
Thank god your family has some taste.

16:35.370 --> 16:37.560
What did patty have to say?

16:37.570 --> 16:40.620
She offered me my job back.

16:41.290 --> 16:42.930
What did you say?

16:42.940 --> 16:44.980
I said no.

16:46.020 --> 16:47.260
Good.

16:47.840 --> 16:50.140
I don't like having her in our lives.

16:50.150 --> 16:52.330
Neither do I.

16:52.340 --> 16:54.700
- You want breakfast?
- Sure

16:55.330 --> 16:57.260
Aw,no.

16:57.270 --> 16:58.680
Who is it?

16:58.690 --> 16:59.960
Lila dimeo.

16:59.970 --> 17:02.050
Don't answer it.

17:02.480 --> 17:04.880
But this is the third time
she's called this week.

17:04.890 --> 17:08.920
Well,we need do something.

17:14.130 --> 17:15.800
We need to talk.

17:20.099 --> 17:21.890
How did it go with judge toomey?

17:21.900 --> 17:24.770
Patty,when are you going
to announce ellen's firing?

17:24.780 --> 17:29.060
I'm-I'm-I'm running around the
office,avoiding people's questions...

17:29.740 --> 17:30.810
And?

17:30.820 --> 17:34.380
And I'm a partner now,and I
need you to treat me like one.

17:34.390 --> 17:37.930
If you have plans for
ellen,i need to know them.

17:37.940 --> 17:39.540
There are no plans.

17:39.550 --> 17:41.780
Then you should tell
the associates that.

17:41.790 --> 17:46.660
Ellen approached a key informant
without our knowledge,and she was fired.

17:46.670 --> 17:48.490
People should know that.

17:48.500 --> 17:50.780
Go announce it.

17:51.570 --> 17:53.190
Thank you.

17:56.270 --> 17:57.980
And,tom?

17:59.520 --> 18:04.810
You're right,you're a partner,i
should start treating you like one.

18:33.780 --> 18:36.020
Goddamn it,gregory,you had one task.

18:36.030 --> 18:38.320
One task,and you screwed it up.

18:38.330 --> 18:40.430
How was I supposed to know the
guy was gonna show up early?

18:40.440 --> 18:42.350
You shouldn't have been in
the condo in the first place.

18:42.360 --> 18:45.380
You were supposed to rent it,leave
the key,and take a goddamn vacation.

18:45.390 --> 18:47.360
I'm sorry,ray.

18:47.370 --> 18:50.790
But I'm telling you,the
girl didn't see anything.

18:50.800 --> 18:55.400
The important thing now
is for you to say nothing.

18:55.410 --> 18:58.630
You just forget any of this
ever happened,understand?

18:58.640 --> 19:00.410
Yes,I understand.

19:02.400 --> 19:05.830
Look,I'm sorry for
raising my voice at you...

19:05.840 --> 19:06.740
It's my fault.

19:06.750 --> 19:08.380
I-I screwed up.

19:09.780 --> 19:12.630
I'm the one who sent you down there.

19:15.210 --> 19:17.120
Listen.

19:18.160 --> 19:22.220
That gift I gave you,for
going down there...

19:22.570 --> 19:24.160
The stock.

19:24.170 --> 19:26.890
Do yourself a favor.

19:28.310 --> 19:30.690
Sell it tomorrow.

19:39.790 --> 19:42.520
Give me a double scotch.

19:42.740 --> 19:44.570
Do you believe this?

19:44.580 --> 19:47.670
I'm staying in a hotel room.

19:48.280 --> 19:50.970
I can't be in that house anymore.

19:51.300 --> 19:55.010
You better get me the best goddamn
divorce attorney in this city.

19:55.020 --> 19:56.840
Of course.

19:56.850 --> 19:59.160
One battle at a time.

19:59.170 --> 20:00.650
Thank you,that's enough.

20:00.660 --> 20:02.110
Art...

20:03.000 --> 20:05.010
we were right.

20:05.280 --> 20:06.530
About what?

20:07.850 --> 20:09.340
George moore.

20:10.790 --> 20:13.020
He sold you out.

20:15.010 --> 20:17.240
Arlington...

20:17.590 --> 20:19.870
gregory malina...

20:21.520 --> 20:25.320
it's all him.

20:37.680 --> 20:39.930
So you're meeting with moore again?

20:39.940 --> 20:41.100
Yeah.

20:41.110 --> 20:45.820
He won't give up frobisher,but
he's going to give us someone else.

20:45.830 --> 20:47.990
You've got him desperate.

20:48.000 --> 20:51.930
He's trying to make the case go
away before it closes in on him.

20:52.330 --> 20:56.040
If moore tipped off
frobisher,that's a crime.

20:56.050 --> 20:58.080
Why shouldn't we just
go after him for that?

20:58.090 --> 21:00.280
Because our clients come first.

21:00.290 --> 21:02.540
Criminal charges would take precedence.

21:02.550 --> 21:06.040
Our case could get pushed
another three years.

21:07.210 --> 21:09.650
We'll get there,ellen...

21:09.660 --> 21:12.000
once step at a time.

21:24.800 --> 21:25.850
here.

21:25.860 --> 21:27.270
What's this?

21:27.280 --> 21:29.940
It should hold you over for a few weeks.

21:29.950 --> 21:31.300
I'm not doing this for money.

